  "title": "Xtra Velvety Mexican Vegetable Curry",
  "description": "A mustardy and velvety Mexican curry featuring Italian seasoning, this dish is perfect for a monsoon evening and is Jain-friendly. It is made with a variety of vegetables and spices.",
